dBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T09:23:06.000Z","msg":"7仔 要講暗號"},{"pid":"fc3393684b056050290b913f42fffba8cc4f51bb","tid":2347684,"uid":80866,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T09:24:15.000Z","msg":"九龍塘站"},{"pid":"79d562e3046b5607424fb3ab95b2bb699f060fc9","tid":2347684,"uid":57424,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T09:27:53.000Z","msg":"美股 GBTC 買下手感，睇下個心臟頂唔頂得順先再研究點買"},{"pid":"6ce8641559a580821a4741f62646cbc6b46839a4","tid":2347684,"uid":49342,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T09:50:07.000Z","msg":"樓主....入市前諗清楚，唔想睇你跳<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n虛擬貨幣大好友，牛頓顧問(Newton Advisors)創辦人Mark Newton周一(28日)表示，<span class=\"red\">比特幣漲勢可能在明年1月初觸頂，故他考慮在未來1、2周內清倉比特幣。</span><br />\n<br />\n線上交易平台eToro美國董事總經理Guy Hirsch認為，比特幣可能<span class=\"red\">面臨監管機構的進一步審查</span>。資產管理公司CoinShares策略長Meltem Demirors亦指出，美國民主黨會帶來挑戰，因<span class=\"red\">拜登傾向加強監管虛擬貨幣</span>，並主張反壟斷政策。<br />\n此外，有「末日博士」之稱的紐約大學經濟學教授魯比尼(Nouriel Roubini)向來亦瞧不起比特幣，直斥<span class=\"red\">比特幣是徹底的騙局</span>，如其他虛擬貨幣都是「屎一般的垃圾」。近日他再度呼籲，一眾<span class=\"red\">虛擬貨幣不應該出現在散戶或機構投資者的投資組合中，並警告比特幣泡沫即將破滅。</span>"},{"pid":"087d7ea522c13aa8f14a86dff90edec506ed5e30","tid":2347684,"uid":41406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T09:55:43.000Z","msg":"兄弟們要走鬼了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa5c68c29bce3ac8ba0513b439f5f7fb2ea72d98","tid":2347684,"uid":70888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T10:03:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f454635c91c97fefdfa4b3f96839997991403092","tid":2347684,"uid":310721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T13:38:49.000Z","msg":"交易廣場個平台，有走鬼檔賣"}]}